{
  "stem": "935.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But nobody told us that we had to write or what we had to write.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On the contrary, we asked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Come on.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We need a card.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We want a card.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We want to send the first card from the first village, and then send the next card from Brussels.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, when John did not show the first night, we were very unhappy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We need a card.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We want to send them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got to Brussels.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're staying in a fabulous villa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what happened then, we were in-- I didn't know where I was, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just know it was not a good place to be.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I somehow got separated from the others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't really know where or when.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But suddenly, perhaps I looked too long at Max, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But suddenly, I heard the steps behind me, and there was nobody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was alone in a courtyard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that moment, I could have escaped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't ask myself till much later, why didn't I?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, first of all, I think I didn't want to admit to myself this was not the way to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was number one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because why not meet a car right there, where they are, in the military or whatever?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Would be a fantastic place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Who would look?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Who would ask?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I wasn't ready to admit this is not the road to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the second reason was, of course, because if you do not know where you are, you also do not know where to go.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Where would I have gone?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had no idea where I was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was all alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
